      "Agent recommends fixing the Program.cs comments to match actual counts, NOT updating docs to match the stale comment.",
      "Agent correctly attributes the discrepancy to v0.9.0 additions (SpectralRetrievalTools, MemoryDiffusionTools, etc.) not reflected in the comment.",
